{"tid":100674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【霸氣】過年小費收$1萬　楊貫一：大客唔會計","createTime":"2017-01-30T08:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T03:23:22.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c790522d293c9fe03ecc7dd00bc9af236a518dd4","tid":100674,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:25:43.000Z","msg":"網上傳出一張銅鑼灣富臨飯店的大年初一收據，金額高達6.2萬元，其中的「加二服務費」就佔1萬元，8隻16頭「阿一吉品鮑魚」則價值3.7萬元。有網民對此價錢譁然，甚至批評收兩成服務費太過份，但有網民則認為富臨作為高級餐廳收費自然昂貴，還取笑大家只是大驚小怪。 <br />\n<br />\n富臨飯店創辦人楊貫一接受《蘋果》查詢時霸氣地說：「6萬幾蚊好平常啫，隨時都有，10幾萬銀一餐都有。」他解釋，富臨出品的鮑魚質素高，來貨價錢本身也高，貨源又少，所以自然要賣得貴，「買返嚟都要咁貴，啲12頭（鮑魚）要5萬幾蚊一斤，咁你賣幾錢一隻呀？啱唔啱呀？有時（我哋）唔係賺好多錢㗎咋&hellip;&hellip;你話貴？貴都有人食呀&hellip;&hellip;食鮑魚要講價值觀㗎！」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170129/large/1485685974_2a67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170129%2Flarge%2F1485685974_2a67.jpg&h=b673f61d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對於收取加二服務費，楊稱每年農曆新年都會這樣做，並不稀奇，「有啲大客嚟到都唔會計呢啲問題，佢都知道㗎啦」。他又補充說：「富臨係鮑魚貴啫，其他嘢都唔係好貴」。 <br />\n<br />\n網民留言： <br />\nAndrew Chui：炒飯菜440 生菜餚240 服務費一萬&hellip;&hellip;果然富貴 <br />\nPhilip Kong：無病呀？ <br />\nAlfa Romeo：食厭咗啦 <br />\nTsoi Christy：食得起有咩問題"},{"pid":"b854f40c5734e33e522941c94e0596a9247bec96","tid":100674,"uid":48460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:31:41.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲食過講下係咪值個個價？<br />\n賣得貴無問題，百貨應百客<br />\n如果貴但食物環境服務差先係問題"},{"pid":"47e6409a7f1b09c04c669d58bbbc37c71de9b705","tid":100674,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:36:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43a6cd47dc0934d5535e2af98a1d79342c892b76","tid":100674,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:43:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無巴絲食過講下係咪值個個價？<br />\n賣得貴無問題，百貨應百客<br />\n如果貴但食物環境服務差先係問題</blockquote><br />\nagree"},{"pid":"1784596b3e2df24556b7ad74c32a93b59680ca45","tid":100674,"uid":69994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:51:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">8隻16頭「阿一吉品鮑魚」則價值3.7萬元</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 16頭？細過田螺，班記者有冇常識</blockquote><br />\n張單上面係咁寫喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n    阿一吉品鮑扣 (16頭)    8    $36800.0"},{"pid":"1227330ddf11a1b884b5bbdfdc026a11a296e824","tid":100674,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:54:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無巴絲食過講下係咪值個個價？<br />\n賣得貴無問題，百貨應百客<br />\n如果貴但食物環境服務差先係問題</blockquote><br />\nagree</blockquote><br />\n未食過<br />\n但我估唔會差得去邊<br />\n俾你係侍應 見到枱客咁闊佬都招呼好d啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d6de27b69e6013dd8b8024f5a4a97f5f3943e5","tid":100674,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:58:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無巴絲食過講下係咪值個個價？<br />\n賣得貴無問題，百貨應百客<br />\n如果貴但食物環境服務差先係問題</blockquote><br />\nagree</blockquote><br />\n未食過<br />\n但我估唔會差得去邊<br />\n俾你係侍應 見到枱客咁闊佬都招呼好d啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有錢佬去得都唔會差<br />\n<br />\n你估大家樂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60188b13cb3743eb7f229d11977bef12cea0904","tid":100674,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:04:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nagree</blockquote><br />\n未食過<br />\n但我估唔會差得去邊<br />\n俾你係侍應 見到枱客咁闊佬都招呼好d啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有錢佬去得都唔會差<br />\n<br />\n你估大家樂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成班見到個價錢嘩嘩聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呀一都話香港大把人去佢到食十萬一餐飯<br />\n人地有錢去食 又覺得值 關你鬼事咩<br />\n可能人地十萬請客食 轉頭簽張千萬合約"},{"pid":"aebe59012ad03cee5b552c4821a8221f6661db5e","tid":100674,"uid":50801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:10:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">8隻16頭「阿一吉品鮑魚」則價值3.7萬元</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 16頭？細過田螺，班記者有冇常識</blockquote><br />\n張單上面係咁寫喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n    阿一吉品鮑扣 (16頭)    8    $36800.0</blockquote><br />\n一斤就十六兩，16頭咪即係一兩?<br />\n輕飄飄都4500蚊隻，可能個汁係阿一d 口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444ec48d34b0981b68a352d7a91602cc3a7b3691","tid":100674,"uid":738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:16:20.000Z","msg":"富臨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a5d8e9203b16b3d779f473f8f11c051eaa4a3b0","tid":100674,"uid":31229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:16:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d893a439a16419b04040650099707c10669f4005","tid":100674,"uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:23:30.000Z","msg":"富臨漁港都食6萬幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8913d025aefd0656c545925f2a16a8b9a19d06","tid":100674,"uid":49260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:24:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢D 海味鮑魚其實成日俾外國人笑<br />\n&quot;呢D竟然係鮑魚?&quot; <br />\n&quot;正常鮑魚不是這種味道的，這是假的吧?&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實又貴又唔係好好食<br />\n真係得D暴發戶先鍾意食呢D野<br />\n<br />\n利申：食過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d07059995ebeb48ccfe58d8dfd6934db4ff26328","tid":100674,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:29:54.000Z","msg":"人地俾得起"},{"pid":"a84797f8e48c50d706151bd13d031f231ad2cec1","tid":100674,"uid":69994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:37:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">8隻16頭「阿一吉品鮑魚」則價值3.7萬元</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 16頭？細過田螺，班記者有冇常識</blockquote><br />\n張單上面係咁寫喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n    阿一吉品鮑扣 (16頭)    8    $36800.0</blockquote><br />\n一斤就十六兩，16頭咪即係一兩?<br />\n輕飄飄都4500蚊隻，可能個汁係阿一d 口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人體70%水份, 你如果曬乾曬都係得 40磅 ~ 50磅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><a href=\"http://gourmetkc.blogspot.hk/2013/04/blog-post_7994.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgourmetkc.blogspot.hk%2F2013%2F04%2Fblog-post_7994.html&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7gHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=6d7dff5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://gourmetkc.blogspot.hk/2013/04/blog-post_7994.html</a><br />\n2013年4月22日 星期一<br />\n&lt;&lt;阿一海景飯店 ~ 《前傳》吉品‧禾麻‧網鮑&gt;&gt;<br />\n相比起網鮑的以口感取勝，吉品就是吃其味道，其濃郁的鮑魚味道也是最引人入勝的地方，加上因為厚身所以甚有嚼頭，所以也是我最喜歡的一款鮑魚。價錢是以最小的24頭賣$1,480至最大的16頭$3,040（另加一），吉品的原產地岩手縣也是前件日本311大海嘯的重災區，所以靚貨是買少見少，有吃要趁手。</span>"},{"pid":"02a860a5ef25675db987265b1e19c5ea405b1a2c","tid":100674,"uid":5590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:39:06.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17389cd181e3929d8fc479fec72b4def21e9aa55","tid":100674,"uid":67329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:39:53.000Z","msg":"人地俾得起又晒得起"},{"pid":"cc26b071726eb5ce31e94c7a63b6dca999cc93ba","tid":100674,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:41:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">8隻16頭「阿一吉品鮑魚」則價值3.7萬元</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 16頭？細過田螺，班記者有冇常識</blockquote><br />\n張單上面係咁寫喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n    阿一吉品鮑扣 (16頭)    8    $36800.0</blockquote><br />\n一斤就十六兩，16頭咪即係一兩?<br />\n輕飄飄都4500蚊隻，可能個汁係阿一d 口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪鳩啦，乾鮑呀，一兩發起左都成三兩啦"},{"pid":"c8e7d8e13b4dc21bd0e26de399734821b3be130a","tid":100674,"uid":54667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:43:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>富臨漁港都食6萬幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n究竟有幾多人唔識分富臨飯店同富臨集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa54433689d291de5179cde51f3a1750afa221fc","tid":100674,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:43:26.000Z","msg":"一早知價錢架啦 有咩好大驚小怪 擺明比有錢人食啦 好多人心態就係有錢都唔食佢啦 咁應該係未夠有錢掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7d38b89b23cbd7cbec77ee6b1db7ae1059463a","tid":100674,"uid":16636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T09:51:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢D 海味鮑魚其實成日俾外國人笑<br />\n&quot;呢D竟然係鮑魚?&quot; <br />\n&quot;正常鮑魚不是這種味道的，這是假的吧?&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實又貴又唔係好好食<br />\n真係得D暴發戶先鍾意食呢D野<br />\n<br />\n利申：食過</blockquote><br />\n攞外國人口味黎評乾鮑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e4cc1327b82346e1b7102c0c9bfdf7c41b3e50","tid":100674,"uid":55464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit